🧠 The Mechanism (what you’re trying to trigger)

A “high-like” state usually comes from a combo of:
	•	Breath → CO₂ / O₂ balance → lightheadedness / body shift
	•	Attention narrowing → reduced inner chatter
	•	Sensory amplification → body feels more vivid
	•	Rhythm → brainwave entrainment (theta/alpha drift)
	•	Expectation → your brain “leans into” the effect

You don’t need substances—you’re just stacking these intentionally.

